					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I was expecting ridiculous, over-the-top lols based off &quot;furry MTF&quot;. Instead, I got some of the best MTF-centric writing I think I've ever seen on this site.</p> <blockquote> <p>Thing is, I'm sure at least a couple of the higher ups are living in a filth pen, barking their orders down at us.</p> </blockquote> <p><em>Like this is just the deepest cut, oh my god.</em></p> <p>And the fucking fursuit head takedown, I can't even.</p> <p>We do not deserve Dog Teeth.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
